name: SparseKind_t
desc: A structure that defines whether the matrix is ordinary, symmetric, or triangular.

items.name: var SparseOrdinary: SparseKind_t
items.desc: An unsymmetric sparse matrix without special structure.

items.name: var SparseTriangular: SparseKind_t
items.desc: A triangular sparse matrix with a nonunit diagonal.

items.name: var SparseUnitTriangular: SparseKind_t
items.desc: A triangular sparse matrix with a unit diagonal.
